9:["$","p",null,{"className":"text-lg text-neutral-600 mb-8","children":"One of our main goals is to promote majority small-scale farmers by marketing their coffee and thereby creating a steady source of income for them. Today, we work with over 50 cooperatives and estates across Kenya's premier coffee regions, ensuring traceability from farm to cup while maintaining the highest quality standards."}]
